            "pub_date": "2025-06-12 15:00:21",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6020084,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉中東情勢升溫、台積電填息失靈 跌182點失守年線",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國公布最新通膨數據溫和，但受美國可能撤離駐伊拉克大使，中東情勢緊張下，美股 11 日四大指數皆收黑下挫，台股今 (12) 日受台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 除息失靈貼息影響，一度下跌逾 200 點，加上電子、金融權值股疲弱，指數開低走低震盪，終場收 22,287.82 點，下跌 182.28 點或 0.81%，成交量略縮為 3,386.22 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020084%2Fl%2Fe06672d02251360fce8e2348c31fc3ff.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉中東情勢升溫、台積電填息失靈 跌182點失守年線。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電因除息前漲多，今日賣壓沉重，股價同大盤走勢開低震盪，終場收 1,045 元，跌逾 1.41%，也影響今天大盤表現，才站上年線一天就失守。據證交所統計，台積電今日除息配發現金股利 4.5 元，影響指數減少約 36.47 點。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股今日表現不一，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、廣達 (2382 -TW) 漲逾 1%；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 跌 2.28%、富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>) 跌逾 2%；航運股的萬海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>)、長榮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2603:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2603\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2603-TW</a>) 則是近期漲多賣壓沉重，跌逾 3%、1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察大盤表現，在權值股表現欠佳下，以油電燃氣類、資訊服務類股表現最佳，包括台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>)、山隆 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>)、台汽電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>)、台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>) 皆收紅；資服類的<a href=\"https://www.wantgoo.com/stock/2468\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">華經</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\"> (2</span>468-TW)、驊宏 (6148 -TW) 受惠 OpenAI 大降價點火上攻，紛紛攻上漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>櫃買 OTC 指數則是逆勢上揚，收紅漲逾 0.32%，收 234.77 點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今天市場呈現熱門題材、中小型類股個別表現，包括全球 AI 晶片龍頭輝達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 執行長黃仁勳在歐洲宣布，未來兩年內將於歐洲設立 20 座 AI 工廠，並於德國打造全球首座工業用 AI 雲端平台，激勵今日雲端資料、散熱概念股的雙鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>) 漲停、奇鋐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>) 漲逾 5%、神達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3706:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3706\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3706-TW</a>) 漲 8%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>分析師表示，台積電貼息判斷是除息前上漲太多，遭到棄息獲利賣壓所致，目前觀察，指數雖然失守年線，但目前多頭趨勢長線仍不變，投資可趁股價拉回時，布局 5 月營收績優及相關熱門題材類股進行操作。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
